window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>As Sahira and Orin move deeper into the Barren Lands, their journey takes them through treacherous places that hide endless surprises and formidable enemies.</p> <p>Faced with continued challenges, they will do whatever it takes to find answers...and freedom.</p> <p>Along the way, new friends emerge, lives are lost, and the secrets unveiled will either bring Orin and Sahira closer or tear them apart forever.</p> <p>Return to the Shadow Realms. A world where vampires feast, lycans love deeply, dark fae seduce, witches cast their spells, dragons rule the skies...and treachery lurks around every corner.</p>"; 
